<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>We will accept AP credit if the student scores a 4 or higher on the AP test.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.grace.edu/academics/academic-catalog" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

 <p class="box-padding-3">
    Additional restrictions and requirements may apply to the policy listed below. For more detailed information, visit the college's AP policy on the Web or contact the college directly.
